special_powers.name: SHORYUREPPA
special_powers.description: Give Ken a double power action. He makes a close combat attack modifying his damage value by +3.

special_powers.name: SHINKU HADOKEN
special_powers.description: Give Ryu a double power action. He makes a range combat attack modifying his damage value by +3.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When Blanka has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: LIGHTNING CANNONBALL
special_powers.description: Give Blanka a double power action. Blanka deals 1 penetrating damage to each adjacent opposing character.

special_powers.name: MIRROR CLAW
special_powers.description: Blanka can use Blades/Claws/Fangs.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When Zangief has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: MIRROR SPIN
special_powers.description: When Zangief makes any close combat attack, he can target all adjacent characters and divide the damage among the hit targets.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When E. Honda has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: SUPER KILLER HEAD RAM
special_powers.description: Give E. Honda a double power action. E. Honda makes up to three close combat attacks as free actions.

special_powers.name: SONIC BOOM
special_powers.description: Guile can use Incapacitate.  In addition to the normal effects, a hit character is dealt 1 damage.

special_powers.name: SENRETSUKYAKU
special_powers.description: Give Chun-Li a double power action. She can use Flurry as a free action, and when she does, she may use Probabillity Control for each attack.

special_powers.name: MIRROR JUMP
special_powers.description: Chun-Li can use Leap/Climb and the Carry ability.

special_powers.name: CANNON SPIKE
special_powers.description: When a character who didn't begin the turn adjacent to Cammy attacks her, modify her defense value by +2. If a character misses Cammy with one or more attacks, deal 1 damage to that character after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: MIRROR CANNON SPIKE
special_powers.description: Modify Cammy's attack value by +1 for each adjacent opposing character.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When Fei Long has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: SHIENKYAKU
special_powers.description: Fei Long can use Quake. When he does, you may choose to have him deal 1 penetrating damage to each hit character instead of the normal damage.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When T. Hawk has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: CONDOR DIVE
special_powers.description: If T. Hawk is given a move action while occupying hindering or elevated terrain, he can ignore hindering terrain and elevated terrain for movement purposes and may make a close combat attack as a free action after the action resolves if he occupies a clear grounded square.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When Balrog has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: TURN PUNCH
special_powers.description: Balrog can use Flurry. For the second attack, he must target a different character and modifies his damage value by +1.

special_powers.name: BLOCK
special_powers.description: When Vega has no action tokens, modify his defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: EX HADOKEN
special_powers.description: Give Ken a double power action. Ken makes a a ranged combat attack. After actions resolve, counter all powers that an opposing character who took damage from this attack possesses until your next turn.

special_powers.name: YOGA INFERNO
special_powers.description: When an opposing character takes damage from Dhalsim's close combat attack, after actions resolve each opposing character adjacent to that character is dealt 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: FLASH EXPLOSION
special_powers.description: Give Guile a power action. Move him up to 3 squares and then make a close combat attack with a locked damage value of 2. A hit character receives an action token. Damage from this attack is penetrating.

special_powers.name: NIGHTMARE BOOSTER
special_powers.description: Give M. Bison a double power action and move him up to his speed value. He can use the Flight ability for this action. If he moved in a straight horizonal or vertical path, after actions resolve, deal 1 penetrating damage to each opposing character occupying a square he moved through.

special_powers.name: METSU SHORYUKEN
special_powers.description: Ryu can use Exploit Weakness.

special_powers.name: TATSUMAKI SENPUKYAKU
special_powers.description: Ken can use Quake.  When Ken uses Quake, after actions resolve, Ken can use the Flight ability, automatically breaks away, and may move up to 3 squares.

special_powers.name: GOSHORYUKEN
special_powers.description: Give Akuma a double power action. He can use Flurry as a free action. If he hits at least one character, after actions resolve he can choose a square within 6 squares and be placed in it and then use Flurry again as a free action.

special_powers.name: THE AWAKENED KILLER
special_powers.description: Damage dealt by Evil Ryu to characters that share a keyword with him is penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: FLASH KICK
special_powers.description: Give Guile a power action. Move him up to 1 square and then make a close combat attack with a locked damage value of 1. A hit character receives an action token.
